hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? cost to make prescription drugs "It was an honor to know Tom Clancy and work on his fantastic books," Ivan Held, President and Publisher of G.P. Putnam's Sons, said in a statement confirming the news. "He was ahead of the news curve and sometimes frighteningly prescient. To publish a Tom Clancy book was a thrill every time. He will be missed by everyone at Putnam and Berkley, and by his fans all over the world."
